@startuml
' Class Diagram for User Registration (Transaction 1.1)

package "Frontend" {
  class RegisterForm {
    +onSubmit()
    +render()
  }
  class AuthStore {
    +register(data)
    +login(credentials)
    +clearError()
  }
  class AuthService {
    +register(data)
    +login(credentials)
    +getProfile()
  }
}

package "Backend" {
  class AuthController {
    +register(req, res)
    +login(req, res)
    +getProfile(req, res)
  }
  class AuthServiceBackend {
    +createUser(userData)
    +findByEmailOrUsername(email, username)
  }
  class Account {
    +id: string
    +email: string
    +username: string
    +password: string
    +type: AccountType
    +isActive: boolean
    +... (other fields)
  }
}

RegisterForm --> AuthStore : uses
AuthStore --> AuthService : uses
AuthService --> AuthController : calls API
AuthController --> AuthServiceBackend : uses
AuthServiceBackend --> Account : persists

@enduml 